  "response": "As of my last update, the average price of a wedding dress typically ranges from $1,000 to $3,000, with many brides spending around $1,500. However, prices can vary widely based on factors such as designer, fabric, style, and whether the dress is custom-made or off-the-rack. High-end designer gowns can exceed $5,000, while more affordable options may be available for under $500. It's worth noting that prices may have changed since then, so it's a good idea to check current trends and retailers for the most accurate information.",
